        <label id="153">
            <property name="fontFamily">"Arial"</property>
            <property name="fontSize">12px</property>
            <property name="textAlign">justify</property>
            <text-property name="text">In terms of Exchange Control Regulations, we have made the above mentioned payment on your behalf without sighting and endorsing the relative Bill of Entry / Import.  You are required to present to us, the original custom stamped Bill of Entry, as proof that the goods have arrived in South Africa. Therefore, it will be appreciated if you could kindly provide the document within 7 days of receiving the original transport document from ourselves.</text-property>
        </label>
